Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================OP============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:51.34,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}任何人都在迷茫中寻觅答案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:11.47,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}曾以为二人同心　时间也可支配
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:19.46,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}当岁月流逝　天空不再湛蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:24.55,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}心与心渐行渐远
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.06,0:02:32.35,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}周而复始　季节循环往复
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:38.92,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}愿时光　永远停留在那瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:45.11,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}二人仍迷茫着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:54.92,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}在天边寻找各自真爱的岁月…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================ED============================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:11.85,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,1500)\an3}曾如此形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:20.94,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,2500)\an3}黄昏却已变色…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:37.28,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}平凡的温柔　让你远去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.53,0:22:45.01,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}被抛弃的心灵　四处彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:53.24,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}这份失落　如果就是生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:57.52,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}我愿在夜空下　从此闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:06.55,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}曾形影不离　黄昏却已变色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:17.77,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}{\be1}至少让我在月光下　静静入眠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 4小时后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.95,0:00:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 你们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.53,0:00:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对阿尔·扎伊里不能掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.74,0:00:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和少尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少…少年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.61,0:00:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 发什么呆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好歹是来当保镖的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里…真的是老虎的根据地？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:00:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么热闹兴旺 看起来很和平
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看起来再和平
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也全都是假象
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.86,0:01:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是 这座城市真正的支配者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.62,0:01:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗者格杀勿论
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.18,0:01:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是扎夫特的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.09,0:01:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沙漠之虎的管辖地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:11.19,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1184,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}宿敌之牙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.51,0:03:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 什么都往里带
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.86,0:03:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里不睡非睡驾驶舱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么时候开始的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.66,0:03:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有也是下地球以后吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前也没那功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得 她是赛的女朋友啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的和基拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.90,0:03:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外？是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话我也没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出问题再那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是先那样再出问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之不太顺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子最近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他作为机师过于优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以至于忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个没接受过任何正规训练的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你一个人的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.28,0:04:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只看见他难以置信的发挥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.29,0:04:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忽视了背后的辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知敌人什么时候会来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时 只有自己能保护舰船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己逼成那样了吧 估计
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么解决办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:04:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能不一定适用于他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 希望这次外出能让他换下心情！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 真羡慕这些年轻人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长还真下得了决心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 虽然只有几个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放大和离开船上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚在基拉屋里过夜的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真打起来 赛怎么可能赢得了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 我也想出去逛逛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当保镖…那家伙真的那么厉害？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？调整人调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有点心神不宁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉一不在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 马上就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事还有我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 下一站
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到 您会来我府上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐拥「水源」 日子过得很滋润啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎伊里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望有生之年不用再见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在「水」的面子上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是倔得像块石头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信念和生命不能相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛伊伯·阿休玛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「水价」天天在涨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 哪口井里的「水」都是「水」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能喝就行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要可以救命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今不打算和你谈论这些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给个话 答应我们的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不答应我们的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说 同胞必须互相帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,细节可以到工厂再谈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分都买齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个叫芙蕾的有点过分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是艾萨利奥的乳液
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是化妆水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里去买这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土耳其烤肉馍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又累又饿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 你也尝尝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浇上一点辣椒酱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉馍上怎么能浇辣椒酱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用酸奶酱才是常识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是常识…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说 对了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不浇酸奶酱是对这道菜的亵渎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素不相识的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没资格对我的饮食习惯说三道四
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 你也尝尝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉馍加辣椒酱才是王道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别带他误入歧途
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么 快走开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:09:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 玩得真开心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同桌的孩子是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在附近的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟老虎有说有笑的死了活该
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始的焰火就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 变成灵魂滚回天上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 混搭也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大采购啊 要办派对？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烦啊 多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你到底是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自坐过来这样那样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 小两口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…到底发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死 调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.18,0:09:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天上的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为蓝色纯净的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.08,0:10:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色宇宙的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用留情 全部干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你 知道怎么用枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 您没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德鲁·巴尔菲鲁特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙漠…之虎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.75,0:10:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水、食物、燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就是 关键的货
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,75mm穿甲弹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曙光社制EQ177磁场阻断器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.87,0:11:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MARK500雷达AI
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 太正了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无话可说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道从哪儿搞来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上还有许多不为人所知的地下水脉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 所谓奇货可居
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:11:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 货还行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 质量没话说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要的都备齐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是自然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请过目
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这金额…我没看错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍贵的水源自然价格不菲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是救命之水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.58,0:12:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城坂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用地球美元支付？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 现在就运走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都什么来头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全跟不上他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我们真的不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰你们喝茶 还有劳出手相救
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的衣服一团糟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能就这么让你们回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 作为我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.99,0:13:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他吗 安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 给女的换身衣裳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辣椒酱、酸奶酱和茶水泼了一身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.06,0:13:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 变成烤肉馍了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡…卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 马上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和安迪等着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对自己煮的咖啡有点自信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先坐下吧 放松点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「迹象01」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见过实物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们为什么喊它叫鲸鱼石呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看这像鲸鱼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那东西怎么看都是翅膀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲸鱼一般没翅膀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实不长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这是来自外宇宙的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地外生命的存在证据
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么喊它鲸鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应该是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个问题不好回答
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 咖啡怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能还不懂如何品尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这成年人的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待有时也是种麻烦 就像它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为找到这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.84,0:15:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说它是希望也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.19,0:15:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能性也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心想 人类能走得更远
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是这场战争最大的根源
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用做了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖听话别动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀这是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 别躲了 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女…孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我只是想说差点忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么区别！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉和卡嘉莉没回来？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:16:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过了约定时间也不出现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛伊伯他们回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电波状况很差
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法和他们直接取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联系上了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.37,0:17:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们回来几个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天街上发生过蓝色宇宙的恐怖袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但做什么都人手不够
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.24,0:17:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕尔下士 呼叫巴基露露中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.71,0:17:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿礼服也很漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样更像你该有的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.25,0:17:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说话就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己呢 真的是沙漠之虎吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么让人穿这种礼服？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是你每次的爱好之一吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选这套礼服的是艾夏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次的爱好是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变装在街上闲逛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放跑居民只烧光城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好眼神 很直率
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别瞧不起人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也认为死了比活着好？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的小伙子 说说你怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样这场战争才会结束？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为机动战士驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太直来直去也不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争没有时间限制也没有得分制度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与体育比赛不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么怎么分出胜负？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以哪里为终点？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到…杀光所有敌人 是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劝你不要动歪脑筋为好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你是个「巴萨卡」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大闹这里不可能全身而退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴萨卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这桩楼里所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都和你一样 是调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看过你的两场战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沙漠里的着地压
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热对流参数
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你在同胞中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也属于相当优秀的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上头说驾驶员是自然人就老老实实相信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没傻到那种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况亲眼见识你刚才的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你出于什么原因选择与同胞作对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但既然是那架机动战士的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你我现在就是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.15,0:20:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是非要一方全灭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.73,0:20:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 今天的你好歹是救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.45,0:20:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也不是战场
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回吧 很高兴和你聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样是好是坏就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战场上再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.32,0:21:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 谁在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.25,0:21:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子还没回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.84,0:21:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 住手傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.22,0:21:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我看到赛那家伙在周围转悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又闹什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.37,0:22:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Next============================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.16,0:23:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共享的温馨时光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.14,0:23:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平和的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.02,0:23:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但流动的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.59,0:23:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使现在瞬间成为过去
